title: Jennifer Lopez Stuns in Chic Style for Another Night Out With Drake-- See the Pic!
text: Jennifer Lopez Stuns in Chic Style for Another Night Out With Drake-- See the Pic! by Jackie Willis 8:24 AM PST, January 18, 2017 Photo: Instagram Jennifer Lopez was giving off major "Jenny From the Block" vibes when she hit the town on Tuesday night. The triple-threat star was spotted heading into Catch LA in West Hollywood, California, wearing a floor-length fur vest, skinny jeans and brown ankle boots. While Lopez showed up alone to the celebrity hotspot, her rumored boyfriend Drake was also seen at the eatery. WATCH: Jennifer Lopez and Drake Snuggle Up to One Another in Intimate Pic An eyewitness tells ET that while en route to Catch LA, Lopez got pulled over by police about a half block away from the restaurant. She still made it to dinner. As for Drake, the eyewitness says the 30-year-old rapper arrived in a limousine that pulled in through the establishment's underground entrance. Photo: AKM-GSI The two continue to fuel romance rumors, the more time they spend with one another . On New Year's Eve, Lopez, 47, attended Drake's Las Vegas show at Hakkasan Nightclub after the two enjoyed dinner with a group of friends. A source later confirmed to ET that they exited the venue together at 2:30 a.m. and were holding hands. Here's more on Lopez and Drake's possible new romance: Additional reporting by Kayley Stumpe.
